// ok refund rule

-------------------- rule

POST /pay?example=range.normal

body:
jpath: $.amount >> {{ range: amount.ok }}

----- response

code:
200

body:
{
    "payment_id": {{ range: payment_id.ok }},
    "status": "ok"
}

-------------------- rule

POST /pay/refund/{{ range: payment_id.ok}}

----- response

code:
200

body:
{
    "status": "ok"
}

